{"tid":1633654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休息撚不如推下聽日三罷啦","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:48:19.000Z","uid":53029,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"836f09c0278a289522074f19f288140a3f3136aa","tid":1633654,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:47:23.000Z","msg":"8/10 三罷"},{"pid":"e254d9a0c9fb6aedd0806bff1ecb589eb55d62d0","tid":1633654,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但黨鐵而家咁撚樣你都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51338f44ea182779b73d228bcaff977dd4c4ade","tid":1633654,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:48:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">又話杯葛？<br />\n又話抗爭？<br />\n繼續俾錢佢賺去出賣港人？<br />\n和理非平時返工唔好再俾正價搭黨鐵！<br />\n無得揀嘅情況例外</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/237n0J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F237n0J0.jpg&h=61248f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0TeRHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0TeRHg.jpg&h=94f567e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFtRTVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFtRTVB.jpg&h=5322f0ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxJ20AB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxJ20AB.jpg&h=c7141e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFpQ9Cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFpQ9Cb.jpg&h=a7156522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果和理非連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話抗爭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日<span style=\"color: red;\">全民三罷</span>！！！<br />\n當十幾歲嘅學生中槍，<br />\n咁多個人冇咗隻眼，<br />\n咁多個義士死諫，<br />\n仲可以正常返工返學？</span>"},{"pid":"2100843d6703f850ce9c514cd1baf10ca72bccb9","tid":1633654,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:48:54.000Z","msg":"8/10 三罷"},{"pid":"c6d767b5e602ec233349a89efcbb4adcac0116d1","tid":1633654,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"罷罷罷"},{"pid":"3e5ce7e45b5048ef62c0d17df8b79618107df7fd","tid":1633654,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:49:25.000Z","msg":"8/10 三罷"},{"pid":"39fa96c6b0e62cf5c069dc825a9fccab36af2eb3","tid":1633654,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:49:41.000Z","msg":"8/10 三罷"},{"pid":"925a1e7ed8517dca6378676ce3c5c03b9f8ec69e","tid":1633654,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:50:13.000Z","msg":"休息撚訓左？？？<br />\n8/10 三罷"},{"pid":"0e9364b2042463fb002b0b72752a1ad399635d1a","tid":1633654,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"8/10 三罷"},{"pid":"4419e3ca2f14bca8ed986320616811f0f64e3c4f","tid":1633654,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:52:21.000Z","msg":"休息撚訓左？？？<br />\n8/10 三罷"},{"pid":"f3b50cfb51697d8a02e638c75543fa9def67a599","tid":1633654,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"休息撚訓左？？？<br />\n8/10 三罷"},{"pid":"1f79a27a2a867f75058d2dea83383d2c9a2566c9","tid":1633654,"uid":53029,"lik